&lt;a href=&quot;http://blog.europeana.eu/2013/11/europeana-celebrates-5-years-and-30-million-objects/&quot; rel=&quot;http://blog.europeana.eu/2013/11/europeana-celebrates-5-years-and-30-million-objects/&quot;&gt;Europeana celebrates 5 years and 30 million.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
